name: CFStringBuiltInEncodings
desc: Encodings that are built-in on all platforms on which macOS runs.

items.name: case macRoman
items.desc: An encoding constant that identifies the Mac Roman encoding.

items.name: case windowsLatin1
items.desc: An encoding constant that identifies the Windows Latin 1 encoding (ANSI codepage 1252).

items.name: case isoLatin1
items.desc: An encoding constant that identifies the ISO Latin 1 encoding (ISO 8859-1)

items.name: case nextStepLatin
items.desc: An encoding constant that identifies the NextStep/OpenStep encoding.

items.name: case ASCII
items.desc: An encoding constant that identifies the ASCII encoding (decimal values 0 through 127).

items.name: case unicode
items.desc: An encoding constant that identifies the Unicode encoding.

items.name: case UTF8
items.desc: An encoding constant that identifies the UTF 8 encoding.

items.name: case nonLossyASCII
items.desc: An encoding constant that identifies non-lossy ASCII encoding.

items.name: static var UTF16: CFStringBuiltInEncodings
items.desc: An encoding constant that identifies kTextEncodingUnicodeDefault + kUnicodeUTF16Format encoding (alias of kCFStringEncodingUnicode).

items.name: case UTF16BE
items.desc: An encoding constant that identifies kTextEncodingUnicodeDefault + kUnicodeUTF16BEFormat encoding. This constant specifies big-endian byte order.

items.name: case UTF16LE
items.desc: An encoding constant that identifies kTextEncodingUnicodeDefault + kUnicodeUTF16LEFormat encoding. This constant specifies little-endian byte order.

items.name: case UTF32
items.desc: An encoding constant that identifies kTextEncodingUnicodeDefault + kUnicodeUTF32Format encoding.

items.name: case UTF32BE
items.desc: An encoding constant that identifies kTextEncodingUnicodeDefault + kUnicodeUTF32BEFormat encoding. This constant specifies big-endian byte order.

items.name: case UTF32LE
items.desc: An encoding constant that identifies kTextEncodingUnicodeDefault + kUnicodeUTF32LEFormat encoding. This constant specifies little-endian byte order.
